<para> <mcss:class xmlns:mcss="http://mcss.mosra.cz/doxygen/" mcss:class="m-note m-default" /></para>
<para><parblock><para>Defined in header: <computeroutput>&lt;pressio/ode_advancers.hpp&gt;</computeroutput></para>
